import React from "react"
import { View, Text, TextInput } from "react-native"
export const LoginScreen = () => {
    return (
        <View style={{
            flex : 1,
            backgroundColor : '#69DFFF'
        }}>
            <View style={{marginLeft : 20, marginTop : 20}}>
                <Text style={{
                    fontSize : 48,
                    fontWeight : '600',
                    color : 'white'
                }}>Log In</Text>
            </View>
            <View style={{
                width : '100%',
                height : '70%',
                backgroundColor : 'white',
                borderRadius : 20,
                alignItems : 'center',
                position : 'absolute',
                bottom : 0,
                padding : 20
            }}>
                <View>
                    <Text>Username</Text>
                    <TextInput
                    style={{
                        width : '90%',
                        height : 40,
                        borderWidth : 1,
                        borderColor : 'lightgray'
                    }}>
                    </TextInput>
                </View>

                <View>
                    <Text>Password</Text>
                    <TextInput secureTextEntry={true}
                    style={{
                        width : '90%',
                        height : 40,
                        borderWidth : 1,
                        borderColor : 'lightgray'
                    }}>
                    </TextInput>
                </View>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
}
